null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1011950, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 2, "EnglishDescription": "It is recommended to visit the holy tomb of Imam Husain (a). Imam Ja’far Sadiq (a) said, “One who offers in the shrine of Imam Husain (a) 10 rakat namaz after Namaze Isha in the form of (2x2) and in each rakat after <Surah Fateha> recite <Surah Ikhlaas> 10 times. After namaz one should seeks Almighty Allah’s protection against Hellfire, if one does this, Almighty Allah will include him with those whom He releases from Hellfire and he will not die before he sees in dream angels conveying to him the good tidings of entering Paradise and security against Hellfire.”", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Mustahab hai keh Qabr Imam Husain (a) ki ziyarat kare. Imam Jafar Sadiq (a) ne farmaya, “Agar koi shakhs Imam Husain (a) ke haram mein 10 rakat namaz, (2x2) rakat karke, jis mein har rakat mein <Surah Fateha> ke baad 10 martaba <Surah Ikhlaas> padhe aur namaz ke baad Allah (swt) se Jahannam ki aag se panah chaahe to Allah (swt) usey un logo’n mein shumaar karega jinhe Jahannam ki aag se azaad kiya hoga aur woh shakhs us waqt tak nahi marega jab tak keh farishte usey Jannat ki bashaarat aur Jahannam se azaadi ki khabar na de-de.”", "UrduDescription": "زیارت حضرت امام حسین ؑ۔ امام جعفرصادق ؑسے پوچھا گیا : جو شخص پندرہویں رمضان کی رات ضریح ِامام حسین ؑکے قریب ہو کر زیارت کرے تو اس کا ثواب کس قدر ہو گا؟ آپؑ نے فرمایا : جو شخص نمازِ عشا کے بعد نافلۂ شب کے علاوہ ضریح مبارک کے نزدیک ۱۰ رکعت نماز پڑھے جس کی ہر رکعت میں <سورۂ فاتحہ> کے بعد ۱۰ مرتبہ <سورۂ اخلاص> کی تلاوت کرے اور نمازسے فارغ ہو کر آتشِ جہنم سے خدائےتعالیٰ کی پناہ مانگے تو وہ اسے جہنم کی آگ سے آزادی عطا کرے گا۔ وہ شخص موت سے پہلے خواب میں ایسے ملائکہ کو دیکھے گا جو اس کوجنت کی بشارت اور جہنم سے امان کی خوش خبری دے رہے ہوں گے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1011951, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 3, "EnglishDescription": "Recite 4-rakat namaz (in form of 2x2 rakats). In 1st & 2nd Rakat after <Surah Fateha> recite <Surah Ikhlaas> 100 times and in 3rd & 4th Rakat after <Surah Fateha> recite <Surah Ikhlaas> 50 times.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "4 Rakat namaz, 2x2 rakat karke, 1st aur 2nd Rakat mein <Surah Fateha> ke baad 100 martaba <Surah Ikhlaas> padhe. 3rd aur 4th Rakat mein <Surah Fateha> ke baad 50 martaba <Surah Ikhlaas> padhe.", "UrduDescription": "اس رات میں ۴ رکعت نماز دو دو کر کے پڑھے جس کی پہلی دو رکعت میں <سورۂ فاتحہ> کے بعد ۱۰۰ مرتبہ <سورۂ اخلاص> پڑھے اور دوسری دو رکعت میں <سورۂ فاتحہ> کے بعد ۵۰ مرتبہ <سورۂ اخلاص> پڑھے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1011953, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 4, "EnglishDescription": "Recite 100-rakat namaz (in form of 2x2 rakats). In each rakat after <Surah Fateha> recite <Surah Ikhlaas> 10 times. In Muqni’ah, Shaikh Mufid has reported Imam Ali (a) as saying, “Whoever offers this prayer, Almighty Allah will appoint for him 10 angels protecting him from his human and jinn enemies and will also appoint 30 angels to secure him against Hellfire at the time of his death.”", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "100 Rakat namaz, 2x2 rakat karke, har rakat mein <Surah Fateha> ke baad 10 martaba <Surah Ikhlaas> padhe. Shaikh Mufid apni kitab Muqni’ah mein riwayat ki hai keh Imam Ali (a) farmate hai keh, “Jo shakhs is namaz ko adaa karega, to Allah (swt) 10 farishto’n ko muqarrar karega jo dushmano se uski hifazat karenge, chaahe woh jinn mine se ho ya ins mein se aur mazeed uski maut ke waqt 30 farishto’n ko muqarrar karega jo usey Jahannam ki aag se bachaye.", "UrduDescription": "۱۰۰رکعت نماز پڑھے جس کی ہر رکعت میں <سورۂ فاتحہ> کے بعد ۱۰ مرتبہ <سورۂ اخلاص> کی تلاوت کرے،مقنعہ میں شیخ مفید ؒ نے امیرالمومنین ؑسے روایت کی ہے : جو شخص اس عمل کو بجا لائے تو حق تعالیٰ کی طرف سے دس فرشتوں کو مقرر کیا جائے گا کہ وہ اس کے دشمنوں (جن ہوں یاانسان) کو اس سے دور رکھیں۔ نیز اس کی موت کے وقت تیس فرشتے آئیں گے جو اس کو جہنم کی آگ سے بچانے کا انتظام کریں گے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSig